    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO1115\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601252463/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601252463&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1115</a></p>\r\n<p>This clear resin protects a weapon from harmful attacks from <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Ooze\">oozes</a>, <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/aberrations/rust-monster\">rust monsters</a>, and similar effects that corrode or melt weapons, rendering the weapon immune for 24 hours. One pot can coat one two-handed weapon, two one-handed or light weapons, or 50 ammunition items. Applying it takes 1 full round. Immersing the weapon in water or similar liquid washes it off.</p>\r\n<p><b>Create</b>: <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) DC 15</p>\r\n<p class=\"header\">Alchemical Power Component</p>\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO9410\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601252226/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601252226&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO9410</a></p>\r\n<p>Weapons and armor aren't the only things bladeguard protects.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class=\"spell\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/w/wall-of-iron\">Wall of Iron</a> (M): For each pot of bladeguard used as a power component, you may designate one 10-foot square of iron wall that has <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Energy-Resistance\">acid resistance</a> 10 and <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Immunity-Ex-or-Su-\">immunity</a> to rusting attacks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
